title.$t: DSA Board Members v.s. People of USA

media$title.$t: DSA Board Members v.s. People of USA

media$description.$t:
Why DSA Board Members denied posting their advertisement on www.deafnewspaper.com?

People of USA wanted Ken Davis to do the DSA Advertisement on his website. But DSA board members denied.  OUCH!

Ken Davis already talked to the President of DSA about People of USA on the DSA advertisement. He has no concerns about it at all. Ken told Jim that he have a hard time to reach his chairperson by email for almost three months. Jim has no concerns about his chairperson at all. 

Ken gave up between DSA board members and People of USA on the DSA advertisement.

Are you ready to buy your advertisement on Deaf Newspaper's website? Are you going to make People of USA to be happy?

Ken believes that his people will buy the DSA combo after posting advertisement on his website.
